'''Fanattic Sports Museum''' (FSM) is a sports [[museum]], dedicated to various types of sports and located in Ecospace Business Park, New Town, [[Kolkata]], [[India]]. Established in January 2017, FSM is known as the first sports museum in Kolkata as well as in West Bengal.

It is an initiative by [[Boria Majumdar|Prof. Boria Majumdar]], an eminent historian, writer, commentator and journalist in association with [[Harshavardhan Neotia]], Chairman, Ambuja Neotia group and consists of sports-related artefacts of various famous sports personalities.

